Package org.Handlers.Logic

package org.Handlers.Logic
  • Class
    Description
    Analyzer<I,O>
    Defines analyzing input data of type I and outputting result of type O.
    AnalyzerFactory
    Factory method for analyzer related classes.
    CFGComparer
    Implements Analyzer and scores the meal's food group stats.
    DatabaseNutrientLookup
    Implementation of Nutrient Lookup using database information.
    FoodGroupAnalyzer
    Implements Analyzer and handles the percentage of the food groups in the meal.
    NutrientAnalyzer
    Implements Analyzer and handles the nutrient distribution of the meal.
    NutrientCalculator
    Handles the calculation and information of nutrients.
    NutrientLookup
    An interface that handles nutrient searching in the database.
    NutritionGuidelines
    Handles nutrient recommendations based off of the CFG and current meal to reach user goals.
    SwapEngine
    Handles swaps within a meal.
    SwapTracker
    Implements Analyzer and handles the nutrient changes due to a swap.
    TrendAnalyzer
    Implements Analyzer and handles the nutrient intake trends over time.
